Unit B - (2) Bedroom, newly renovated, separate kitchen & living room, Unit C - (2) Bedroom, separate living room & kitchen, Unit D - (4) bedroom, Bi-Level, (2) Bath.  Tenants pay electric & oil (1 unit), Landlord pays cold water.  There is an assumable mortgage on this property with low interest rate!!
